Title: Adiabatic motion of two-component BPS kinks

Authors: A. Alonso Izquierdo, M.A. Gonzalez Leon, J. Mateos Guilarte and M. de

la Torre MayadoComments: 15 pages, 9 figures. Final version to appear in Phys. Rev. D

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D66 (2002) 105022

The low energy dynamics of degenerated BPS domain walls arising in ageneralized Wess-Zumino model is described as geodesic motion in the space ofthese topological walls.